From 4b297fed03279b1c5431d42354ece5c8ef77d364 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: jmat <jens.mattke@raab.de>
Date: Sun, 12 Apr 2026 14:21:08 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 4/6] 004-ui-customization: Compact header, context ring,
 auto-approve in settings
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Compact single-row task header (no accordion)
- Circular context window ring with hover details
- Hidden Plan/Act toggle in footer
- Simplified navbar (New Task, History, Settings only)
- Auto-approve controls moved from footer to Settings → Features
- Hidden cost bubbles in history
- Thinking indicator in messages area
- Scroll behavior fixes
- Theme CSS additions
